========== ESSENTIALS ==========================================================

Remove the MAX_ATTEMPTS limit

Use `appdirs` to store `.masterhash` and `.pwds` in a standard place

Enforce good master passwords

Use hashlib.pbkdf2_hmac with high iteration count for salted hashing

Salsa20 + HMAC for authenticity check of `.pwds`

Use `secrets.choice(lst)` to generate new passwords




